item.title: My compiler wont work
item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

If you have JDK 6 update 21 than try this

@echo off title Compiler "C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

Or

@echo off title Compiler Javac *.java pause
